&lt;p>&lt;code>echo STRING | curl -F-=\&amp;lt;- qrenco.de&lt;/code>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Crear Commit Aleatorio</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/crear-commit-aleatorio/</link><pubDate>Wed, 09 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/crear-commit-aleatorio/</guid><description>&lt;p>Puedes usar estos comandos para añadir aleatoriedad a diferentes programas.&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Commits aleatorios
&lt;code>curl -s https://whatthecommit.com/index.txt&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Chistes de padres
&lt;code>curl https://icanhazdadjoke.com&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>Puede usarse por ejemplo en un &lt;strong>alias&lt;/strong>:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># Para chezmoi&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">alias&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">chzu&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;chezmoi git add . ; chezmoi git -- commit -m &amp;#34;$(curl -s https://whatthecommit.com/index.txt)&amp;#34; ; chezmoi git push&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># Para git&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">alias&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">gitodo&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;git add . ; git commit -m &amp;#34;$(curl -s https://whatthecommit.com/index.txt)&amp;#34; ; git push&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>El Tiempo En El Terminal Oneline</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/el-tiempo-en-el-terminal-oneline/</link><pubDate>Wed, 09 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/el-tiempo-en-el-terminal-oneline/</guid><description>&lt;p>Muestra la previsión metereológica para la ciudad que elijas durante los próximos días&lt;/p>
